title: BBC Love and Drugs on the Street Girls Sleeping Rough Series 1 2
description: Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Lily Murray, published by BBC in 2017 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/e/e0/Love-and-Drugs-on-the-Street-Girls-Sleeping-Rough-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Eye-opening stories of the daily lives of women sleeping rough on Brighton's streets. 2) Mothers and Lovers Paige has had a fresh start in a hostel but her daughter is being put up for adoption, while Maria has succumbed to the grip of heroin addiction, having had two children removed from her care. With around three-quarters of mothers sleeping on the streets having had kids taken away, can they break the vicious cycle?
